N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 79.41 - Interference with, or unauthorized starting of, aircraft prohibited

State Regulations

No person shall interfere with the operation of any
aircraft at the airport, or start any engine of such aircraft without the
operator's consent. Notes
